Module  : Remember Username
Version : 1.1.0
Author  : Maurice Makaay

This module will store the Phorum username that was last used in
a cookie. When entering the login screen, the username will be
automatically filled in, based on this cookie.


Install:
--------

- Unpack the archive;

- Move the directory "remember_username" to the directory "mods"
  within your Phorum installation;

- Login as administrator in Phorum's administrative interface and
  go to the "Modules" section;

- Enable the module "Remember Username".

